Is NetSurf Dead?
text:
Since 2007 NetSurf has had multiple releases per year, until 2017 where it slowed to one release per year. The last release was May 2020.

Anyone close to the project know why the effort slowed down? I know it's a monumental task to make a web browser but even so as it is it has it's uses.
